PersonalMission.Name: SPG-14: One of Us!
PersonalMission.Description: Cooperation is the key to victory for the whole team. Highlight the enemy vehicle you are aiming at for your allies to immediately bring down fire on it once it has been stunned or immobilized. Remember: a lone soldier can hardly make a battle.

Primary.Conditions:
•  Stun for 100 seconds (personal/Platoon)
or
•  Allies must cause 600 HP of damage to the enemy vehicle immobilized by you
